data.description: SELLER HAS 3% ASSUMABLE FHA LOAN, WILLING TO TRANSFER TO FIRST AGREEABLE OFFER!  WON’T SEE THAT RATE AGAIN FOR A LONG TIME!  SAVE HUNDREDS PER MONTH WITH THIS RATE! Very Motivated Seller! $20,000 recent price reduction!  Schedule a Showing today!  Gorgeous brick 2-story home nestled in sought-after Suwanee! This home's elegant interior finishes and beautiful open floor plan are sure to capture your heart. The floor plan opens to a 2-story foyer and features a spacious kitchen with granite countertops and a cozy breakfast area. Natural light brightens and adorns this wonderful home's hardwood floors throughout. Your gatherings will surely extend out to the spacious patio and backyard. Upstairs you will find the 4 spacious bedrooms including the wonderful owners' retreat. The master bathroom is complete with a jacuzzi tub and a separate shower. Enjoy the highly sought-after community which features a private pool, tennis, basketball, and clubhouse for private gatherings! This property is situated in an outstanding location - quick access to Atlanta, Downtown Duluth, Downtown Suwanee, I-85, I-985 as well as close proximity to shopping, restaurants, parks, and walking distance to top-rated schools! Seller will provide a 1 year Home Warranty policy for buyers upon closing! Come and tour today, you will love this fantastic home for many years to come!
